ment.\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    It’s your responsibility to provide the original logo to manage the brand if the logo needs to be designed or redesigned for high quality then it will be entertained as extra charge depending upon the requirement.\n                </li>\n            </ol>\n        </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p>\n        <span style=\"color:hsl(0,75%,60%);\">Note if you want to upgrade the plan then you can find it on our website at </span><a href=\"https://paradiseit.com.np\"><span style=\"color:hsl(0,75%,60%);\">https://paradiseit.com.np</span></a><span style=\"color:hsl(0,75%,60%);\">. And video shoot will be once a month.</span>\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Payment Terms and Conditions</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        For the services rendered in accordance with this Agreement the Client consents to pay the Service Provider as an initial of the month. The payment is scheduled to pay monthly for taking the service.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <span style=\"background-color:hsl(60,75%,60%);\"><strong>The payment will be NRs. 20,000/- per month.</strong></span>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        If the client wishes to boost a particular post then the spent amount should be paid as per the exchange rate of the specific day.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n        <strong>If client needs VAT bill then 13% VAT will be payable.</strong>\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Service Inspection</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        The client must inspect the service provider\'s completed work before receiving any compensation. The Client shall have the right to alert the Service Provider of any defective or incomplete Services done by the Service Provider according to this Agreement and the Service Provider shall quickly repair such work within a reasonable period of time.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Return of Goods</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        All property given by the Client including but not limited to cleaning supplies, clothing, equipment and any other goods shall be returned by the Service Provider upon the termination of this Agreement.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Timeliness</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        Service Provider acknowledges that all Services must be completed on time as mentioned on terms and conditions.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Confidentiality</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        The Service Provider understands and accepts that any financial and accounting records, lists of the Client\'s property including amounts paid, customer and client lists and any other information and data about the Client\'s business are secret (\"Confidential Information\"). Therefore, during the term of this Agreement or after its termination, Service Provider shall not, unless the client has previously given written approval, use or disclose any confidential information for the advantage of anyone other than the client, except disclosures required to be made to advance the business of the Client and information that is public record.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Safety</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        The Service Provider shall be solely responsible for protecting its employees, subcontractors, material suppliers and all other staff from the risk of death, injury or bodily harm resulting from or in any way related to the Services or the location where it is being performed (the \"Work Site\"). This responsibility shall be at the Service Provider\'s expense. In addition, the service provider consents to follow all guidelines established by federal law and government of Nepal. Any fines, fees or penalties imposed shall be the exclusive responsibility and liability of the Service Provider.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Rule of Law</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        The laws of the State of Government of Nepal shall govern this Agreement and be applied in its interpretation.\n    </p>\n</section>\n<section>\n    <h2>\n        <span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Severability</strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <p>\n        The parties acknowledge that if any part of this Contract is invalid, the remaining sections will still be fully enforceable.\n    </p>\n</section>', '2024-07-04 07:59:40', '2024-07-07 09:45:55'),
(17, 'Future Dream Web Design', '20240704080814-wezmstndvt-future-dream-web-design', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '<h1 style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>Web Development Agreement</strong></h1><section><h2><span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>Introduction</strong></span></h2><p>This Service Agreement (here referred to as the \"Agreement\") is made by and between Future Dream Educational Consultancy,<strong> Putalisadak Kathmandu Nepal</strong> (here referred to as the \"Client\") and Paradise InfoTech of Thamel-26 Kathmandu Nepal (here referred to as the \"Service Provider\") who are each referred to as a \"Party\" and who collectively as the \"Parties.\"</p><p>Therefore in consideration of the commitments and agreements made by both parties here the Client hereby engages the Service Provider to perform services in accordance with the conditions that the Parties have hereby agreed to:</p></section><section><h2><span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>THE SERVICE</strong></span></h2><p>The following is the list of commitments to be made by the service provider as Digital Management referred to as the \"Service\" moving forward.</p><p>While providing the Service the Service Provider shall to the best of their abilities comply with the Client\'s policies standards and regulations including local state and federal laws.</p></section><section><h2><span style=\"color:#0959a2;\"><strong>TERMS AND CONDITIONS ON WEB DEVELOPMENT</strong></span></h2><p><strong>Website Design and Development for futuredreamnepal.com</strong></p><p>Basic Includes: Home, Slider, Services, Gallery, Notice/Updates, Downloads, Sidebar Pages, Contact Page, Google Map, Social Networking Integration, and more built on own CMS.</p><ul><li>Dynamic Backend &nbsp;</li><li>Notice updates and news (Blogging)</li><li>Proper customization &nbsp;</li><li>Information page</li><li>All the required features &nbsp;</li><li>Integrations</li><li>Database Management. &nbsp;</l