(1, 'Rajendra Rijal', '29', '<p>I am really impressed by the quality of services I received from Paradise - IT Solution. You were right on schedule, charged reasonable prices, were professional and courteous in dealings, and delivered service well before time. I have received a very good support to scale up my website and emails system. My system security has increased because of you and I will definitely use your services again and would like to recommend other to take IT and email hosting solution.&nbsp;</p>', 'CEO - KIEC', 1, 1, '2023-11-10 08:16:46', '2023-12-15 17:34:32'),
(2, 'Pawan Singh Rajput', '30', '<p>Firstly, I would like to thanks for doing a wonderful job. Working with Paradise It solution is very easy and friendly. Understanding the need of the customer is the most important thing and they understand our needs , and have designed website accordingly.&nbsp;<br>Looking ahead to continue work with you in coming years too.<br>Best Wishes for &nbsp;the success of your company</p>', 'Senior Coordinator - Wendy House School', 2, 1, '2023-12-15 17:37:41', '2023-12-18 09:42:29'),
(3, 'Gaurab Raj Baral', '31', '<p>Paradise-IT Solution is one the best IT companies in Nepal for all of our IT needs.&nbsp;</p><p>Their Email Hosting services (Google Workspace) is really impressive.&nbsp;</p><p>I am using their services for my 4 companies with 100% satisfaction.&nbsp;</p><p>I would like to strongly recommend Paradise for anything related to IT.</p>', 'CEO -  Trinity Education, Pokhara', NULL, 1, '2023-12-15 17:39:29', '2023-12-18 09:42:05'),
(4, 'Madhav Kumar Kandel', '32', '<p>Our experience with Paradise has been nothing short of exceptional. From the initial consultation to the final delivery, their team demonstrated a profound understanding of our unique needs and goals.&nbsp;</p><p>The level of creativity and innovation they brought to our project exceeded our expectations, resulting in a visually stunning and highly functional digital presence.&nbsp;</p>', 'CEO - Flights Gyani Pvt. Ltd.', 4, 1, '2023-12-15 17:44:26', '2023-12-15 17:45:04');

